LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:erf diffusion solution"

\end_inset

.
 To show how the concentration profile evolves with time, we have included
 values of 
\begin_inset Formula $\ell_{a}^{D}$
\end_inset

 in the plot.
\end_layout

