\begin_inset Formula $e_{xy}$
\end_inset

, with the shear modulus 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 defined as the ratio of shear stress over shear strain:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\tau=G\frac{u}{d}\label{eq:shear modulus definition}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


