\begin_inset Formula $bG/2\pi d$
\end_inset

.
 The interplanar spacing, 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

 is comparable to 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

.
 (We're not going to worry about the exact numerical factor here, since
 we're just aiming to get an approximate expression for 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau_{crss}$
\end_inset

