 In either case, 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{n}_{d}$
\end_inset

 = 0.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
For an edge dislocation, the magnitude of 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{n}_{d}$
\end_inset

