 The dislocation moves a distance 
\begin_inset Formula $\ell$
\end_inset

 in this case.
 Because the length of the dislocation is 
\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

, the total force applied to the dislocation is 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{s}^{\tau}w$
\end_inset

, and the energy required to translate it by a distance 
\begin_inset Formula $\ell$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{s}^{\tau}w\ell$
\end_inset

.
