\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At equilibrium the net force acting on the dislocation is zero (
\begin_inset Formula $F_{s}=0$
\end_inset

).
 This occurs when the applied stress is equal to a critical value that we
 refer to as 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau^{*}$
\end_inset

: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
