\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{2}$
\end_inset

in this case we need to know the following interfacial energies:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{w}$
\end_inset

: the surface free energy of water
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{o}$
\end_inset

: the surface free energy of the oil
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{ow}$
\end_inset

